      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. This example retains its factory-spec Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and M Variable Differential Lock, delivering visceral mechanical feedback. The chassis remains structurally flawless with documented subframe reinforcement and fresh OEM bushings. Recent comprehensive service includes a precise valve shim adjustment and VANOS system overhaul, ensuring optimal cam timing and compression across all cylinders. Finished in pristine Titanium Silver with original VIN tags on all panels, this is a turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist.",
