    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a true showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously preserved since day one. The exterior finish is absolutely flawless, boasting a deep, glass-like luster without a single swirl mark, rock chip, or blemish. Inside, the cabin remains in 'time capsule' condition; the premium leather seats still retain their factory scent and firm support, with no signs of wear on the bolsters or touchpoints. Mechanically, this car is peerless. It has been garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and serviced exclusively by certified specialists using only OEM parts. Every button, switch, and electronic feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. The engine bay is pristine, reflecting a lifetime of preventative maintenance and obsessive care. This isn't just a used car; it is a collector-grade example for the most discerning buyer who demands perfection in every detail.",
