    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty in person. It looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely flawless inside and out! I've taken incredible care of it, and it's honestly a dream to drive. If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
